OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FLewis Capaldi cancels shows
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fto 'rest and recover'      
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Lewis Capaldi has cancelled a series of
OL,6, upcoming gigs to "rest and recover"    
OL,7, over concerns about his health.        
OL,9,FThe Scottish singer said he was        
OL,10,Fstruggling "mentally and physically"   
OL,11,Fand wanted to be at his best and return
OL,12,Fto the stage at Glastonbury on 24 June.
OL,14,FCapaldi, 26, had been scheduled to play
OL,15,Fconcerts in Glasgow, Dublin, London and
OL,16,FNorway over the coming weeks.          
OL,18,FIn an Instagram post, he said he needed
OL,19,Fa break from touring in order to be    
OL,20,F"Lewis from Glasgow for a bit".        
